From cf9f480af95b408ac0ce768cf622b9f3c972bab2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 20:10:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Embed cleaned-up 7.41 patch notes template into index.html

Replace the old hand-made patchnotespage_* markup inside #dota-page-container
(shown after the passcode + match-found sequence) with the semantic structure
from the cleaned-up dota/ assets, trimmed to a workable template:

- All 5 section headers and all 10 group headers from the real 7.41 notes
- Every unique element: note lines (plain, nested, spacer/elbow, hidden
  bullet), all 12 stat-icon variants, aghs scepter/shard notes, info
  tooltip, image preview with zoom icon, New/Reworked/Bold badges
- Five full hero blocks (Bane, Invoker, Lifestealer, Templar Assassin,
  Zeus) chosen to cover every within-hero change type and all four
  attribute icons, with their complete change lists preserved
- Item and neutral-item/creep samples including New and Reworked items

Styling comes from the new dota-patchnote.css, a copy of dota/main.css with
every selector scoped under #dota-page-container so nothing leaks into the
portfolio styles. The superseded patchnotespage_* rules are removed from
common.css; the microheader/rootfooter markup and styles are kept as-is.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
